{"tid":751420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估國家？  婚禮排隊揸姊妹波","createTime":"2018-07-22T00:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T01:13:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":357,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"49d6e9cb56a310c86164db7fdc24fdcb8b23c9b8","tid":751420,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"中國人辦婚禮，卻常常出現低俗婚鬧，繼上周的「軍令指插」之後，本周又有新篇章，這次是上演「揉饅頭」。<br />\n影片所見，一名癡漢參加婚禮，竟對一名穿著蘋果綠禮服的「伴娘」襲胸。癡漢直接把手伸進女子的胸部裡，不斷地左搓右揉，拍攝影片的男子還直問他：「大不大啊？」只見揉奶的癡漢一臉淫相，死死抱著女子的胸部不放，但女子也沒有反抗的意思，繼續讓癡漢摸奶。隨後被窩裡突然跳出一名黑衣男子，也等著排隊搶著要「揉饅頭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180722/1395901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180722%2F1395901&d=d9SJeEKS6pdKvdtGCHFHOW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=18765f5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180722%2F1395901&h=006a5345\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180722/1395901</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180722/640_1fcc16a9940aa4b15938023c0d8dcd3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180722%2F640_1fcc16a9940aa4b15938023c0d8dcd3e.jpg&h=2622d287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關鍵字: 41j , 痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02150562aeeb6e8e3ee3d7d65db0ccf352d96c10","tid":751420,"uid":132038,"like":357,"dislike":225,"score":132,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae3ae3cfbecb60cc7c7e3ab024b012cf5a31c94e","tid":751420,"uid":44175,"like":204,"dislike":3,"score":201,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"原本以為個tag係樓豬自己加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/